{"title":"苦煞画家","authors":["池北偶","朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦煞画家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶  诗  朱根华  画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画家名气够大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人竞相索画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要画幅山水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要画幅梅花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的喜欢鹰鹫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人酷爱鱼虾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了画能到手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总要说尽好话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并非真会鉴赏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是附庸风雅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有收藏保值，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有卖个高价。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸手诸公太多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在难以招架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好不停动笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这可苦煞画家。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}